I get past enrage by learning when it usually happens....gauging how fast the mob is going down....and nuking him past that 10% of his health (in essence leap-frogging him over his enrage)...my group in the maze was so amazed (sorry couldn't resist) at my ability to do this that they conscientiously strove to keep clear of my bolts...<br>
